nodes.text: Kuna's Eye was a location in the Moddell sector of the Outer Rim Territories. Prior to the Battle of Endor in 4 ABY, Corporal Ractivelle of the Stardust unit featured Kuna's Eye in a map as part of a Rebel Alliance report on the navigation of the Moddell sector in preparation for the Rebel Alliance's attack on the second Death Star.

Before the Battle of Endor, the map of the Moddell sector and the accompanying reports were archived in The Rebel Files, a data archive safeguarding secret rebel documents and information. In 34 ABY, The Rebel Files were rediscovered and ultimately given to the Resistance.
Kuna's Eye was first mentioned in Star Wars: The Rebel Files, a canon boxed set and reference book first released in 2017 and authored by Daniel Wallace.
